{"tid":1951412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[魔鬼在細節]支那抵港須檢疫5月初失效　賣港賊：屆時恢復部分交通","createTime":"2020-03-31T03:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T04:22:04.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c80946349c5d287301efcc1d8aa2ea1baa166805","tid":1951412,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:26:30.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，內地新型肺炎確診個案大幅減少，但目前未有計劃放寬對內地入境者的限制。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥在行政會議前說，內地近日確診個案大多數是輸入病例，但現階段不會放寬相關入境限制及重開來往內地的關口。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，疫情不穩定仍有變數，加上收緊入境限制後，經港珠澳大橋及深圳灣入境人士數目顯著下跌，因此沒有很大需要重開關口。<strong>另外，根據《若干到港人士強制檢疫規例》（第599C章），當局會對所有內地抵港者發出檢疫令，強制有關人士必須實行家居檢疫14天；但此規定有時限，到5月初便會失效，屆時也會自動恢復部分交通。 </strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517910-20200331.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517910-20200331.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=755a0a7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517910-20200331.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fecf16b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517910-20200331.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"11edcc0519b10da5146477dec9f2d54df784091c","tid":1951412,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"Pish 下先"},{"pid":"cf32f77f745da44b20d34ff7f7fb9e821fef0ff4","tid":1951412,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:34:23.000Z","msg":"好事，攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14bb1a3fd32e79a4f857d40e288bf4a63439a13","tid":1951412,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"開始日日都有還押幾個月手足上庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1951351\" data-auto-link 